==English==
===Noun===
'''cupboardy'''

#  Cupboard like - from the famous british show Little Britain. The word is used when Kenny Craig, the stage show hypnotist fooled his mom into thinking it was a real word when they were playing Scrabble. However, Craig's hypnotic skills are not what they seem as it turns out she was just being kind and allowing him to win (it was on a triple word score and gave him 103 points).